Unisex accessible bathroom inside cat area — as you enter cat area, it’s on the right toward back of the room (past the employees only door with the cat door in it).
Unisex bathroom in cafe — as you enter, it would be toward the back of the room on the left, past the cat area door.
comment:
Unisex accessible restroom is inside the cat area. (Requires reservation/payment).
Additional unisex bathroom is available in cafe (I don’t believe payment is required, but still would be a nice courtesy to buy a drink, you know?)

name: Thrive Counseling Center

name: MacNab Transit Terminal

comment: This was a wonderful discovery. They also have free wifi, and plugs to charge your phone. They also have two gender bathrooms for men and women. It wasn’t until I went there a couple times before I realized that there was a Gender Neutral bathroom.
